devdoc.details: A contract that manages a whitelist of addresses.

addToWhitelist(address).details: Adds a member to the whitelist.

params.member: Address of the user to be added to the whitelist.

isWhitelisted(address).details: Checks if a member is in the whitelist.

params.member: Address of the user to check.

returns._0: bool Indicates if the user is whitelisted.

removeFromWhitelist(address).details: Removes a member from the whitelist.

params.member: Address of the user to be removed from the whitelist.
